{"tid":469633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"諸位,你們知道ASMR什麼嗎?","createTime":"2017-11-15T13:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T15:26:25.000Z","uid":139613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30b7005e522f17a231f3efd1f4426fb399b0e4b8","tid":469633,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"自發性知覺經絡反應（英語：Autonomous sensory meridian response，縮寫ASMR）<br />\n也稱自發性知覺高潮反應，是一種對於視覺、聽覺、觸覺、嗅覺等其他知覺，顱內、頭皮、後背以及四肢等周邊部位受到刺激而產生愉悅反應的感知現象。<br />\n<br />\n換言之 聽落會有高潮嘅感覺 個人建議 要專心聽 唔好諗其他野 咁就有可能會對某D聲有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不妨留低你鐘意嘅聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween youtube長期都有ASMR嘅直播 其中一個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YERDYhKo3Ok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYERDYhKo3Ok&d=BYZh%2BNvFhhioL873difohgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=dd15d1e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YERDYhKo3Ok</a>"},{"pid":"b71434a05305ec4979e15bda3ea4e4be137b2c68","tid":469633,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912a2b49ef538ab68215adf46a2ce038149262f6","tid":469633,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係個腦高潮<br />\n唔係真係高潮左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dab8bd0fc6989cd901a1d8d73946a6a8e523eb1","tid":469633,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜聽森美講<br />\n<br />\n原來要帶耳筒式先得<br />\n<br />\n入耳式要聽3d錄音先feel到<br />\n